Package sage.model.loader.ogreXML

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OgreXMLAnimationParser
    OgreXMLAnimationParser parses animation data found in an OgreXML .skeleton file and populates data in a hierarchy of Model3DTriMeshes.
    OgreXMLMaterialParser
    OgreXMLMaterialParser is used to parse OgreXML .material files to associate textures with submeshes.
    OgreXMLParser
    OgreXMLParser is used to parse OgreXML files containing geometry, material, and animation data and turn them into a Group of Model3DTriMeshes to be rendered.
    OgreXMLVertexBoneAssignment
    OgreXMLVertexBoneAssignment represents the weight a specific Joint contributes towards animating a vertex.
